    "In the incentive conditions, participants were told they would receive a bonus should their overall reappraisal quality be in the top 25% of all reappraisals in their condition.",
    "We generated ratings in the same way as we did in Study 1.",
    "We had three hypotheses for this study (preregistration: https://osf.io/4t8qc).",
    "Hypothesis 1 was that GPT would outperform humans, similar to Study 1.",
    "Hypothesis 2 was that incentivized participants would improve humans' reappraisal quality and reduce the difference between humans and GPT."
  ],
